a12.title: Fund Swiftsol’s TG & Twitter Bot Updates + Ongoing Support for BBL / BoostDAO Marketplaces & Collection Info
a12.description:
This proposal requests a payment of 3,000 LUNA from the DAO treasury to compensate community member @Swiftsol for the development and ongoing maintenance until 03/15/26 of two critical bots that enhance the visibility and functionality of the Alliance DAO NFT collection across Telegram and Twitter.

@Swiftsol has delivered the following bots:

1. Marketplace Sales Bot (Telegram)

Tracks real-time sales from both Backbone Labs and BoostDAO marketplaces, including:

Sale price and marketplace origin

NFT image and ID

Floor price (FP) reporting for both marketplaces. NOTE due to the amount of list token options in Boost the bot will only report LUNA, USDC, and ampLUNA listings at this time. 

Floor status (broken vs. unbroken)

Total number of NFTs listed across marketplaces

2. About Bot (Telegram)
Provides quick-access information about the collection, including:

Collection summary

Key links (marketplaces, staking, governance, social links etc.)

3. NFT Tracker Bot (Telegram)
Tracks and reports live data such as:

Minted vs. unminted supply

Broken NFTs (DAO-broken vs. user-broken)

Tradeable vs. Locked NFTs

Staked NFTs in DAODAO and Enterprise.


The total amount requested is 3,000 LUNA, covering:

1,500 LUNA (250 USD) for the Telegram bot work.

1,500 LUNA (250 USD) for the Twitter bot work.

This compensation includes past development work and guarantees ongoing support and maintenance through March 15, 2026.

These tools strengthen our collection’s transparency, community engagement, and marketplace coverage all are critical pieces as we continue to expand Alliance DAO's presence and credibility.
~@~@~@~

a21.title: Stake 20 Pixel Lions, Whitelist $ROAR & Finalize 1.5B ROAR for 4,500 LUNA OTC Deal
a21.description:
This proposal authorizes the following actions to advance Allaince DAO’s partnership with Lion DAO and Pixel Lions:
	1.	Stake 20 Pixel Lion NFTs in PL DAO.
	2.	Whitelist $ROAR token in our DAO treasury for visibility and tracking.
	3.	Whitelist Pixel Lion NFTs for treasury display.
	4.	Approve and execute an OTC token deal with PixeLion a (the stewardship wallet for Lion DAO & Pixel Lions), involving:
	•	Alliance DAO contributing 4,500 LUNA.
	•	PixeLion / Lion DAO contributing 1.5 billion $ROAR.
	•	Tokens distributed to both DAOs per the agreed allocation.

Upon passing prop in both DAO’s, Alliance DAO will hold 1.5 billion $ROAR from this OTC deal, in addition to 1.5 billion $ROAR already received from the prior NFT partnership (total: 3 billion $ROAR).

Once ROAR is in our treasury a follow-up proposal will deploy the 3B $ROAR in line with the results from our recent community poll in Telegram.

a22.title: Deploy 3 Billion ROAR acquired through Alliance made with Lion DAO / Pixel Lion.
a22.description:
This proposal outlines a detailed plan for the strategic deployment of the 3 billion $ROAR tokens acquired by the Alliance DAO through an over-the-counter (OTC) NFT and token swap. The proposed allocation is a direct result of a community poll conducted in the official Alliance DAO Telegram chat, ensuring the strategy aligns with member consensus. The plan involves splitting the $ROAR holdings into three equal tranches to stake for governance influence, provide single-sided liquidity, and create a traditional liquidity pool pair with $LUNA.

The Alliance DAO has successfully acquired 3 billion $ROAR tokens. To ensure these assets are utilized effectively and for the benefit of the DAO, a community poll was initiated to gauge sentiment on the optimal deployment strategy. The poll presented several options, balancing governance participation, yield generation, and risk exposure (specifically impermanent loss). This proposal formalizes the winning strategy from that poll.

Proposal Details

Based on the poll results, this proposal seeks authorization to deploy the 3 billion $ROAR tokens as follows. The allocation reflects the top-voted option, which received 42% of the community vote.

The 3 billion $ROAR will be allocated in three equal parts:

Tranche 1: Staking with Lion DAO (1 Billion $ROAR)

Action: 1 billion $ROAR (33.3% of the total) will be staked with Lion DAO.

Objective: To gain a voice in $LUNA governance. This strategic position helps protect and enhance the value of Alliance DAO's rewards and strengthens our influence within the ecosystem.

Tranche 2: ampROAR/ROAR Liquidity Pool (1 Billion $ROAR)

Action: 1 billion $ROAR (33.3% of the total) will be deposited into the ampROAR/ROAR single-asset liquidity pool.

Objective: To generate yield with mitigated risk of impermanent loss. This provides a stable return on our assets without exposure to the price volatility of a secondary token.

Tranche 3: LUNA/ROAR Liquidity Pool (1 Billion $ROAR)

Action: 1 billion $ROAR (33.3% of the total) will be paired with $LUNA to provide liquidity in the $LUNA/ROAR pool.

Objective: To deepen liquidity for the $ROAR token and capture potentially higher yields from trading fees and incentives, accepting the associated risk of impermanent loss.

Implementation of the $LUNA/ROAR LP
Additionally this TG poll determined the preferred method for creating the $LUNA/ROAR LP position. The community voted decisively on the following method:

Match $ROAR with $LUNA from Treasury: The DAO will commit an equivalent value of $LUNA from the treasury to match the 1 billion $ROAR deposit. This requires an additional expenditure of $LUNA from the treasury but was unanimously supported (4 votes to 0) over zapping into the pool with only $ROAR.

This proposal is a direct execution of the community's will. The three-pronged strategy represents a balanced and diversified approach:

Diversification: It spreads treasury assets across staking, low-risk liquidity providing, and high-yield liquidity providing, avoiding over-concentration in a single strategy.

Community Mandate: The allocation directly reflects the outcome of the primary poll, and the implementation detail for the $LUNA/ROAR pool is based on the result of the secondary poll.

Strategic Alignment: The plan achieves multiple DAO objectives simultaneously: active governance participation, stable yield generation, and contribution to ecosystem liquidity.

Conclusion
By approving this proposal, the Alliance DAO will activate its newly acquired $ROAR assets in a manner that is strategic, diversified, and most importantly, directed by its members. We request the community's support to execute this well-vetted plan.

a23.title: Stake 10,000 LUNA with the Lion DAO Validator
a23.description:
This proposal seeks community approval to stake 10,000 $LUNA from the DAO's liquid treasury holdings. The objective is twofold: to put idle assets to work earning staking rewards derived from on-chain inflation, and to strengthen our ecosystem partnership by delegating these funds to the Lion DAO validator. This action will make a portion of our treasury productive while maintaining significant liquidity for future opportunities. 

The Alliance DAO treasury currently holds approximately 75,000 liquid $LUNA. While maintaining liquidity is essential for operational flexibility, a significant portion of these assets are currently idle and not generating any yield. Staking $LUNA is a fundamental, low-risk mechanism for participating in network security and, in return, earning staking rewards.

Furthermore, this action provides a direct way to support our partners at Lion DAO, who operate a trusted validator. Delegating to partner validators strengthens the decentralization of the network and reinforces the collaborative spirit of the "pride" ecosystem. This proposal balances prudent financial management with strategic community support.

Proposal Details
Action: Stake 10,000 $LUNA.

Source of Funds: The $LUNA will be sourced from the Alliance DAO's main treasury wallet, which currently holds ~75,000 liquid $LUNA.

Delegation Target: The entire 10,000 $LUNA delegation will be made to the official Lion DAO validator.

Impact on Treasury: This will move approximately 13.3% of our liquid $LUNA into a staked, yield-bearing position. Over 65,000 $LUNA will remain liquid and available in the treasury.

Productive Asset Utilization: Staking allows us to convert idle $LUNA into productive assets. The DAO will begin earning passive income through on-chain staking rewards, growing the value of our treasury over time.

Strategic Partnership: Delegating to the Lion DAO validator is a powerful, capital-efficient method to support a key ecosystem ally. A stronger and more secure Lion DAO benefits the entire community.

Low-Risk Yield: Native on-chain staking is widely considered one of the safest ways to generate yield in the ecosystem. By choosing a reputable validator like Lion DAO, we further minimize potential risks.

Prudent Allocation: Staking 10,000 $LUNA is a measured step. It allows us to begin generating yield while keeping the vast majority of our $LUNA holdings (~87%) liquid for other investments, operational expenses, or market opportunities.

Risks & Considerations
Unbonding Period: Staked $LUNA is subject to a 21-day unbonding period. During this time, the delegated 10,000 $LUNA will be illiquid and cannot be accessed immediately.

Slashing Risk: All proof-of-stake networks have a slashing risk, where a small portion of staked funds can be lost if a validator node goes offline for an extended period or acts maliciously. We are confident in the operational security of the Lion DAO validator, making this risk minimal.

Conclusion
This proposal presents a clear opportunity to enhance treasury yield and support a key partner with minimal risk. It aligns with sound financial management principles by putting otherwise unproductive capital to work. We urge the community to vote YES to stake 10,000 $LUNA and strengthen both our treasury and our alliances.

a26.title: September 2025 Rewards Claim
a26.description:
Summary
This proposal authorizes several routine treasury management actions. It includes claiming all available rewards from our Terra Luna Alliance (TLA) positions and our LUNA staking with the Lion DAO validator. Additionally, it executes a previously approved but missed action to increase our arbLUNA lock. The goal is to efficiently compound our DAO's assets and maintain the health of our treasury.

Background
As part of our regular operations, we periodically claim rewards from our various DeFi and staking positions to maximize returns. This proposal bundles these standard actions for efficiency. It also addresses an oversight from the last proposal batch, where 183 arbLUNA were successfully converted but not added to arbLUNA LOCK #600 as intended. This proposal will complete that final step.

Proposed Actions
If this proposal passes, the following transactions will be executed:

Increase arbLUNA Lock: Use the 183 arbLUNA currently in the treasury to increase the stake in arbLUNA LOCK #600.

Claim TLA Deposit Rewards: Claim all accrued rewards from our TLA Deposits, which will be received as ampLUNA.

Claim TLA LP Vote Rewards: Claim all accrued rewards earned from our LP incentive voting on TLA.

Claim TLA Rebase Rewards: Claim the periodic TLA rebase rewards.

Claim LUNA Staking Rewards: Claim all available staking rewards from the 10,000 LUNA delegated to the Lion DAO validator.

Justification
Passing this proposal is a standard housekeeping measure that ensures our assets are working effectively for the DAO. It allows us to compound our holdings, secure our earnings, and correct a minor operational oversight from the previous cycle.
